{"tid":1063868,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【明日戰記】古天樂 4億巨製強戰外星生物　全新預告終極大佬現身","createTime":"2019-03-16T05:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T05:55:59.000Z","uid":82268,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e48cacfcb4a6c631f5b47120056a8a52a2864cc2","tid":1063868,"uid":82268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T05:59:10.000Z","msg":"期待已久的香港科幻大製作《明日戰記》，由古天樂、劉青雲、劉嘉玲、張家輝、姜皓文、謝君豪等主演，新晉導演吳炫輝執導，一年前推出首預告引起全城哄動。事隔一年再有第二條預告見街。《明日戰記》耗資港幣4.5億製作，全新預告不止繼續展現高超的本土特技，還有進一步交代劇情，其中張家輝角色更似是不簡單。<br />\n<br />\n《明日戰記》的故事設定於2055年，地球受到具攻擊性的外星異種藤蔓「潘朵拉」入侵，空氣以及水源都受到污染，人類似乎只可以依靠由古天樂、劉嘉玲、劉青雲及姜皓文的拯救隊伍去尋求希望，更要面對張家輝所代表的「天幕計劃」謎團。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lMFJijxmUFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlMFJijxmUFo&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnMmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=9bff4da2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lMFJijxmUFo</a><br />\n實入場睇支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726beb1e25fc58428cee45c667a005dabd71a4a5","tid":1063868,"uid":198497,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:00:26.000Z","msg":"又係張家輝，古天樂，劉青雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65508953ad56c86d601a0b5351204ea20af8c79f","tid":1063868,"uid":59711,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"話曬都係一個新嘗試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好過千篇一律既警匪片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c124cabb661b54bf531f84d1eea39883425a7f6","tid":1063868,"uid":59711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"726beb1e25fc58428cee45c667a005dabd71a4a5","tid":1063868,"uid":198497,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:00:26.000Z","msg":"又係張家輝，古天樂，劉青雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class